  "info": {
    "title": "UKG Pro WFM",
    "description": "UKG Pro Workforce Management (formerly UKG Dimensions) REST API. Covers persons, schedules, timecards, punches, paycodes, time off, accruals, leave, hyperfinds, and tenant information across the Common Resources, Scheduling, Timekeeping, and Accruals domains.",
